Redefining the "Monday Blues" from a sun-dappled courtyard in Fontainhas. 🌿💻

As remote work and the digital nomad culture continue to grow, the demand for spaces that blend productivity with peace is at an all-time high. At Vida & Vinho Café, we designed our space to be a functional hub for creators, tech professionals, and entrepreneurs visiting or living in Goa.

With high-speed Wi-Fi, plenty of power outlets, and a steady supply of specialty Goan-grown cold brews to fuel you up for those long email replies, we are proud to host a vibrant community of professionals every week.

Looking for a change of scenery for your team's next deep-work session? Drop by this week or send us a DM to reserve our quiet corner table.

